# CI/CD Flow

```
Developer Push Code
        │
        ▼
     GitHub
        │
        ▼
     Jenkins Pipeline
        │
        ├── Checkout Code
        ├── Build Docker Image
        ├── Push to DockerHub
        └── Deploy to Kubernetes
        │
        ▼
     Kubernetes Cluster
        │
        ▼
     Running Application
```

